            "description": "Activision had asked us to create a social MMO for their Hero franchise (Guitar Hero, DJ Hero, Band Hero). This social MMO, named Hero World, was to be linked with their Hero retail games. For example, a user in Guitar Hero could create a character, and then continue with that same character in Hero World. Sadly Activision decided to kill their Hero franchise so the project was canceled.\n\nI was responsible for all the environments together with Jimmy de Meza. He did all the important buildings like the Neptunes store. While I created the rest of the map. Including lighting, rendering and managing the \u201cMaster\u201d file. Interns helped us with small props and some of the interiors.",
